00:09:27.791 --> 00:09:30.427
Hey! Bulma'nın evi nerede?

00:09:30.427 --> 00:09:32.996
Eh? Bulma...?

00:09:32.996 --> 00:09:34.731
Evet.

00:09:34.731 --> 00:09:38.835
